We compute Born radii (ai)numerically for each charged atom

i in the solute. This is done by evaluating Gpol(if)or each such

atom with a continuum dielectric medium using a finite difference

method (see supplementary material) assuming that all other

atoms are neutral and displace the dielectric. Given Gpl(i),the

